    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning, showroom-quality vehicle! This car is in mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, making it a rare find for anyone seeking a flawless, top-tier driving experience!",
