    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some fading on the clear coat in sun-exposed areas. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from years of use. While the engine and transmission are running well, the car will likely need routine maintenance soon, such as new tires and a brake service, to remain in peak operating order. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any frills.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
