    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in an exemplary state of preservation, reflecting a standard of care typically reserved for discerning private collections. From the flawless coachwork to the pristine interior appointments, every detail affirms its showroom-quality status. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that defines mechanical perfection and aesthetic excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
